name: Pixel Arse : Ultimate piece
description:
This is the last piece in Pixel arse series. 
If you want to have this in your collection  collect 3 or more pieces of Pixel arses and I will send you this one for free. Please read the rules.
 Rules : 
1. only primary market sales count.
2. if less than 3 pieces is availabe you might as well collect 2 or 3 editions of the same piece.
3.if less than 3 editions are available in general the last person to collect the rest (2 or 1 last edition) also wins the piece.
4. I will burn the remaining editions once all Pixel arse are sold out on Primary.
5. I will keep tracking the sales but if you collected your 3 editions and I didnt send you the ultimate pice. dm me on Twitter on Instagram.
